		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Opt Out isn’t Just for One Day</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Recently there was a lot of news around an &ldquo;opt out day&rdquo; with respect to the American TSA using scanners to take nude pictures of travelers. The idea was that if people opted out on one of the busiest travel days in the USA it would bring lines to a stand-still and perhaps cause the</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2010-12-15 10:18:07">15 Dec 2010 - 10:18AM</time>
		</span>
			</span>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>	

            <div class="content">
                <div class="social-wrapper" id="social-sharer">
